<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.1">
<l>ceyya tāmaraik kaṇṇa ṉāyula kēḻu muṇṭa vavaṉkaṇṭīr</l>
<l>vaiyam vāṉa maṉicar teyva maṟṟu maṟṟu maṟṟu muṟṟumāy</l>
<l>ceyya cūḻcuṭar ñāṉa māyveḷip paṭṭi vaipaṭait tāṉpiṉṉu</l>
<l>moykoḷ cōtiyō ṭāyi ṉāṉoru mūva rākiya mūrttiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who as red lotus-eyed Kṛṣṇa swallowed the seven worlds, see,</l>
<l>becoming earth, sky, humans, gods and others and others and all,</l>
<l>revealing himself as red pervasive glowing knowledge, he created these, and after</l>
<l>along with excellent light he became the form that is the one triad.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
